  Syntax: twowayfeweights count_usa class_id grntyr treat,

. di "          type(feTR) controls(count_for) summary_measures"
          type(feTR) controls(count_for) summary_measures

. di ""


. cap noisily twowayfeweights count_usa class_id grntyr treat, ///
>     type(feTR) controls(count_for) summary_measures

Under the common trends assumption,
the TWFE coefficient beta, equal to 0.1505, estimates a weighted sum of 7056 ATTs. 
7056 ATTs receive a positive weight, and 0 receive a negative weight.
------------------------------------------------
Treat. var: treat       # ATTs      Σ weights  
------------------------------------------------
Positive weights        7056        1.0000      
Negative weights        0           0.0000      
------------------------------------------------
Total                   7056        1.0000      
------------------------------------------------

